language translation and learning app that will translate the spoken words of a person in real-time so that it can be understood by a different language speaking person. This app would not only translate word/sentences but will also help to learn new languages, Improve pronunciation and communication skills. Learning app can save a lot time and money. Fun exercises will make learning a lot easy and user can learn without getting bored. which will make learning fun.
Firstly this app will feature a function of live voice translation people can translate words from any language to native. Secondly language learning people will learn language by short tasks, quiz, and fun exercises. Moreover vocabulary trainer which helps to improve vocab, Grammar review this will help user to investigate what has to practice to improve skills and Listening comprehension user will listen to native short videos which will help in understanding words and pronunciation. Additionally a premium user tab in which people can buy premium membership which will features online classes with experts and 24x7 doubt solving and support.